column1: IF ccr_cortisone_d is MF 2 AND ccr_thdoc_d is MF 2 AND ccr_cortisol_d is MF 0 AND ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 2 THEN 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
IF ccr_cortisol_d is MF 0 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_pt_d is MF 0 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 0
IF ccr_thaldo_d is MF 0 AND ccr_a_cortol_d is MF 1 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0
IF ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 2 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 0  2_Normal is 1  3_Surpoid is 1  4_Obese is 1  5_ExtremeObese is 1
